<h1 class="heading-title">
  
    
    
    
    
      
  The impact of artificial light at night on nocturnal insects: A review and synthesis


    
  
</h1>

  <div class="article-citation" style="display:inline-block;">
  
    <span class="article-source">
      
<span class="journal" style="display:inline-block;">Ecol Evol</span><span class="period">. </span><span class="cit">2018 Oct 23;8(22):11337-11358.</span>

